{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":51,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_leng_bing_yu","speaker_name":"冷冰鱼","listener":"char_gong_sun_hong","text":"先莫管那是什么，且亮你的天龙棍，接我的震天笔。","tone":"厉声","chapter":33,"line_start":2,"line_end":4},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_hong","speaker_name":"公孙红","listener":"char_leng_bing_yu","text":"阁下莫非已等不及了？","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":33,"line_start":6,"line_end":6},{"speaker":"char_leng_bing_yu","speaker_name":"冷冰鱼","listener":"char_gong_sun_hong","text":"不错，冷某等着你一战，已等了六年之久。只要你与我交手，无论你是否有理，冷某都已不放在心上。","tone":"认真","chapter":33,"line_start":8,"line_end":12},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_hong","speaker_name":"公孙红","listener":"char_leng_bing_yu","text":"也好。","tone":"平静","chapter":33,"line_start":14,"line_end":14},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_hong","speaker_name":"公孙红","listener":"char_leng_bing_yu","text":"还不放马过来？","tone":"豪迈","chapter":33,"line_start":16,"line_end":16},{"speaker":"char_leng_bing_yu","speaker_name":"冷冰鱼","listener":"char_gong_sun_hong","text":"你既要与冷某动手，天龙棍何在？","tone":"疑问","chapter":33,"line_start":18,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_hong","speaker_name":"公孙红","listener":"char_leng_bing_yu","text":"就在这里。","tone":"淡然","chapter":33,"line_start":22,"line_end":22},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_hong","speaker_name":"公孙红","listener":"char_leng_bing_yu","text":"面临决战，为何狂笑？","tone":"疑问","chapter":33,"line_start":30,"line_end":30},{"speaker":"char_leng_bing_yu","speaker_name":"冷冰鱼","listener":"char_gong_sun_hong","text":"名震天下的天龙棍，竟是如此一条短棒！如此一条短棒，竟能列名于破云震天笔之上，却叫冷某怎能不为之失笑","tone":"狂笑","chapter":33,"line_start":32,"line_end":36},{"speaker":"char_leng_bing_yu","speaker_name":"冷冰鱼","listener":"char_gong_sun_hong","text":"你笑什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":33,"line_start":38,"line_end":38},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_hong","speaker_name":"公孙红","listener":"char_leng_bing_yu","text":"名动天下，号称文武兼通、博学无双的少庄主，竟是如此有眼无珠，却叫某家怎能不为之失笑？","tone":"狂笑","chapter":33,"line_start":40,"line_end":42},{"speaker":"char_leng_bing_yu","speaker_name":"冷冰鱼","listener":"char_gong_sun_hong","text":"此话怎讲？","tone":"怒怒","chapter":33,"line_start":44,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_hong","speaker_name":"公孙红","listener":"char_leng_bing_yu","text":"阁下既称博学，岂不闻拙中之巧，返璄归真，方是天下之大巧大妙？某家这一根短棒之中，内蕴天地变化之机，外藏鬼神莫测之变，岂是凡俗兵刃可比，又岂是你等这些凡胎肉眼所能揣测？","tone":"严肃","chapter":33,"line_start":46,"line_end":50}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
